{
  "stem": "13623.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's one of the prisoners, no different than anybody else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's still-- he is still with us at that point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some of the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we were together-- we hadn't been separated at this point yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were still together with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, there was no-- no way, there was-- we-- we didn't even many times knew when-- when Shabbos was or when a holiday was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just-- there was no way of doing any sort of observing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- the rabbi was still with us at this point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of the people that-- from the town, some adults from the town would go over to the rabbi and they would ask him, can we eat some of that soup that they're giving us?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they were concerned and they-- it's not kosher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he tell-- he told the people, everybody is on his own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a matter of survival, if it's-- it's a survival of the fittest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you just do what your heart tells you to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, we-- we get assigned to different work details.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of us are assigned to dig, what I would call, integration ditches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're giving-- we're going to work with pick and shovel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Regardless of the age, regardless of the condition of the prisoner, we're given a quota.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Each team, one guy with a pick and one guy with a shovel, has to dig a so-- something, a ditch that is so long by so wide and so deep.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- that-- that was in centimeters and meters, whereas we're in inches and feet today.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- I can't translate it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If you didn't finish the quota today, you got the same quota tomorrow, and you had to finish from the day before.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
